## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **alteplase 1996 → 4.5-hr 2008** = first + only FDA AIS thrombolysis (NINDS 1995 + ECASS-3 2008). 30년 동안 단일 thrombolytic agent. quantum-VQE 의 plasminogen-fibrin specificity 가 직접 fit.
2. **tenecteplase 2024 SETT-3 / TIMELESS / TRACE-2** = stroke 적응증 FDA 표지 미정 2026-05-08 — 그러나 AHA 2024 가이드라인 + 다수 stroke center 가 이미 off-label primary. fibrin-specific + bolus + 더 긴 window 가 alteplase 대비 advantage.
3. **mechanical thrombectomy 2015 5 RCT (MR CLEAN/ESCAPE/EXTEND-IA/SWIFT-PRIME/REVASCAT)** = AIS large-vessel-occlusion 표준 단일 paradigm shift. 2018 DAWN + DEFUSE-3 6-24h late window + 2024 ANGEL-ASPECT/SELECT2/RESCUE-Japan LIMIT large core 확장. stent retriever 약물 아님이지만 약리 paradigm 전환.
4. **DAPT (clopidogrel + aspirin) 21-90일 minor stroke + TIA (CHANCE 2013 + POINT 2018)** = TIA 즉시 dual antiplatelet 표준. CYP2C19 LoF 는 ticagrelor 대체 (THALES 2020).
5. **DOAC 4종 (apixaban + rivaroxaban + dabigatran + edoxaban) 2010-2015** = warfarin 대체 Afib stroke prevention. cross-iag intersection + factor XIa next-gen (abelacimab/asundexian/milvexian) reduced-bleed candidate.
6. **nimodipine 1988** = SAH vasospasm 표준. cerebral-selective L-type Ca2+ block. SAH 5-14일 routine.
7. **neuroprotection 30+ trial fail history** — NMDA antagonist (aptiganel/selfotel) + free radical scavenger (NXY-059 SAINT-II) + Mg2+ (FAST-MAG) + ICAM-1 (enlimomab EAST) + nerinetide (ESCAPE-NA1 2020). single-target neuroprotection 가설 null. quantum-VQE 의 PPI multi-target rescue 한정 chance.
8. **3K3A-APC NeuroNEXT positive Phase 2** = activated protein C 변형 — 첫 modern neuroprotection positive signal. anticoagulant activity 제거 + cytoprotection 유지. RHAPSODY 후 Phase 3 expanded.
9. **fluoxetine FOCUS / EFFECTS 2018 negative** = SSRI post-stroke motor 회복 small null. citicoline US 미승인 + Spain/JP 표준 — 효과 임상적 의미 limited.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, acute stroke 임상 의미 한정.

